pliance </span><span class="symbol_value" data-highlight="cms"><span class="symbol">C<span class="sub">MS</span> </span><span class="value"><b>1152</b></span></span><span class="units" data-highlight="cms">µm/N</span></li><li><span data-highlight="vas">Equivalent volume to the compliance </span><span class="symbol_value" data-highlight="vas"><span class="symbol">V<span class="sub">AS</span> </span><span class="value"><b>1.68</b></span></span><span class="units" data-highlight="vas">L</span></li><li><span data-highlight="rms">Mechanical resistance </span><span class="symbol_value" data-highlight="rms"><span class="symbol">R<span class="sub">MS</span> </span><span class="value"><b>0.21</b></span></span><span class="units" data-highlight="rms">N·s/m</span></li><li><span class="name_value" data-highlight="surround_material"><span>Surround material </span><span class="value"><b>Santoprene</b></span></span><span class="no units" data-highlight="surround_material"></span></li></ul><h3>Dimensions</h3><ul><li><span class="name_value" data-highlight="size_in"><span>Nominal diameter </span><span class="value"><b>3</b></span></span><span class="units" data-highlight="size_in">″</span></li><li><span class="name_value" data-highlight="size_mm"><span> </span><span class="value"><b>76</b></span></span><span class="units" data-highlight="size_mm">mm</span></li><li><span class="name_value" data-highlight="weight"><span>Net weight </span><span class="value"><b>0.202</b></span></span><span class="units" data-highlight="weight">kg</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="measured"><div class="tabs-container"><div class="menu"><div class="item selected" data-menu-item="/TangBand/W3-532SQ/TangBand_W3-532SQ_(Frequency_response_+_Impedance).png">SPL &amp; Impedance</div></div><div class="tabs crosshair"><div data-tab="/TangBand/W3-532SQ/TangBand_W3-532SQ_(Frequency_response_+_Impedance).png" class=""><img src="/TangBand/W3-532SQ/TangBand_W3-532SQ_(Frequency_response_+_Impedance).png" alt="Ta